title: Windows Server 2008 x64
description:
This is the ISO of Windows Server 2008 x64 Edition. 

Volume License key is not included.

This is not hacked, cracked, or even touched.

Installable options are:

Server 2008 Standard
Server 2008 Enterprise
Server 2008 Datacenter Edition
Server 2008 Standard (Core Only)
Server 2008 Enterprise (Core Only)
Server 2008 Datacenter Edition (Core Only)

This DVD contains the 64-bit editions, no 32-bit options.
